5 C. The fee for such plates shall be Thirty-five Dollars
6 ($35.00) per year of renewal and shall be in addition to all other
7 registration fees provided by the Oklahoma Vehicle License and
8 Registration Act. The fee shall be apportioned as follows through
9 June 30, 2023:
10 1. Twenty Dollars ($20.00) per year of renewal or any other
11 amount as provided in this title of the fee shall be apportioned as
12 provided or deposited in a fund as specified within the paragraph
13 authorizing the special license plate;
14 2. Eight Dollars ($8.00) per year of renewal of the fee shall
15 be deposited in the Tax Commission Reimbursement Fund to be used for
16 the administration of the Oklahoma Vehicle License and Registration
17 Act. Beginning January 1, 2023, Eight Dollars ($8.00) per year of
18 renewal of the fee shall be deposited in the Service Oklahoma
19 Reimbursement Fund to be used for the administration of the Oklahoma
20 Vehicle License and Registration Act; and
21 3. Any remaining amounts of the fee shall be apportioned as
22 provided in Section 1104 of this title.
